        <h2>Understanding the Beauty of Koi Fish</h2>
        <p class="date">Published on November 13, 2024</p>
        <img src="~/images/koi01.jpg" alt="Beautiful Koi Fish in a pond">
        <p>Koi fish are admired worldwide for their vibrant colors and symbolic meaning. Originating from Japan, they are known for their beauty, grace, and resilience. Different varieties of Koi, like Kohaku, Sanke, and Showa, each have unique colors and patterns that make them highly desirable among fish enthusiasts.</p>
    </section>

