        <p class="date">Published on November 1, 2024</p>
        <img src="~/images/koi02.jpg" alt="Koi Fish Care">
        <p>Caring for Koi fish requires knowledge about pond maintenance, water quality, and feeding schedules. New Koi owners should ensure that their ponds have proper filtration and aeration systems. Feeding them a balanced diet with occasional treats can also enhance their color and vitality.</p>
    </section>

