        <p class="date">Published on October 15, 2024</p>
        <img src="~/images/koi04.jpg" alt="Koi Fish Breeding">
        <p>During the breeding season, Koi fish become more active and may exhibit behaviors such as chasing each other around the pond. Providing adequate space and shelter for breeding Koi can help improve the survival rate of young fish. It’s essential to monitor water quality closely during this time as well.</p>
